==Description==
The '''Odd Keystone''' is a type of [[Underground|Underground Item]].

==Details==
The Odd Keystone has a value of 6 [[Diamonds]] {{Diamonds}} when sold. It can also be traded in Daily Deals.

==Mine Layout==
The Odd Keystone appears in the Underground as a 4x4 sized object.<br><br>
[[File:OddKeystoneMine.png|100px]]

==Acquisition==
Odd Keystones can be found in the [[Underground]], traded for with the [[Berry Master|Hoenn Berry Master]], and as Loot in [[Dungeons]].

